data.description: This 2-story home in Longs Ridge community is move-in ready and offers you an open floor plan, spacious living areas, game room, and 3 bedrooms all up for privacy. Your chef will enjoy the spacious island kitchen with updated quartz countertops and stainless steel fridge. You'll love the easy care wood-looking ceramic tile on the 1st floor. Beautifully canopied backyard is the perfect setting for outdoor entertaining. NEISD schools include Madison HS. Easy access to Loop 1604.
